This application allows you to access various information about GitHub repositories and users through the GitHub API.

It currently is in very early development stages, so it is still simple and some features may be missing.

New in v0.2:
* Repository Network List
* Show more fork information
* Repository Commit Log
* Repository owner displayed in repository lists
* Cleaned other stuff up

TODO:
